Author: orthofuckyrself
Text: >Everyone else is having a good time, snacking and sipping and hey – I’m doing it, too! But am I doing it *too*  much? Do I really need to celebrate THIS much? Does this even count as  celebrating at this point? Am I overeating? Is this bingeing? Am I just  having a good time? ***What is happening!?***  Dang. Too real.   &#x200B;
